th":"/jYcvdfOce89Vzisi0pOK9bLfIgT.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":4.722},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/rxO7i4WidAJy38s2x1LMDKf1qOB.jpg","iso_639_1":"ko","vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":"2026-02-21T13:17:45.549+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"Fureru","runtime":107,"tagline":"I want us to be together, always⎯","homepage":"https://www.crunchyroll.com/series/GMTE00348901/fureru","overview":"Childhood friends find a creature with mysterious powers that pushes them to discover the bonds that tie the three students together."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":107,"tagline":"謎の生き物<ふれる>が繋いでくれた友情―それは永遠に続くはずだった。","homepage":"https://fureru-movie.com","overview":"同じ島で育った幼馴染、秋と諒と優太。  東京・高田馬場で共同生活を始めた三人は  20歳になった現在でも親友同士。  それは島から連れてきた不思議な生き物「ふれる」が持つ  テレパシーにも似た力で  趣味も性格も違う彼らを結び付けていたからだ。  お互いの身体に触れ合えば心の声が聴こえてくる－  それは誰にも知られていない三人だけの秘密。  しかし、ある事件がきっかけとなり、秋、諒、優太は、  「ふれる」の力を通じて伝えたはずの心の声が聴こえないことに気づく。  「ふれる」に隠されたもう一つの力が  徐々に明らかになるにつれ、  三人の友情は大きく揺れ動いていく－"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"후레루.","runtime":107,"tagline":"말하지 않아도 서로의 마음을 알 수 있었던 우리들의 이야기","homepage":"","overview":"서로의 모든 것을 안다고 믿었던 스무 살의 여름, 그때 우리는 우정이 영원할 거라 믿었다.  어린 시절, 신비한 생물 ‘후레루’를 만나 서로 닿기만 해도 속마음을 알 수 있게 된 소꿉친구 아키, 료, 유타.  스무 살이 되어 도쿄에서 함께 살아가던 그들은 예기치 못한 감정에 부딪히며, 점점 서로를 오해하게 된다.  그러던 어느 날, 그들을 이어주던 ‘후레루’의 숨겨진 비밀이 드러나고, 세 사람의 우정은 깊은 흔들림에 휩싸이게 되는데…"},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"Fureru","runtime":107,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Aki, Ryo e Yuta cresceram em uma pequena ilha japonesa com Fureru, um pequeno ouriço amarelo com poderes misteriosos. Agora, na casa dos 20 anos e buscando um novo começo em Tóquio, o trio tenta construir uma nova vida enquanto mantém seu companheiro incomum longe dos olhares curiosos. Mas, à medida que os poderes de Fureru despertam, emoções reprimidas e antigas tensões ressurgem, levando a amizade deles a um território imprevisível."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"触碰你","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"自幼在岛上相识相伴成长的挚友秋、谅和优太，20岁一起来到东京开启全新的同居生活。三人从岛上带来的神秘生物「碰碰」，形似刺猬并且有着类似心灵感应的能力，能让身体接触的人实现思想互通。初入社会性格与志趣迥然的三人，因为「碰碰」的存在一直维持着平稳和谐的友谊，然而随着「碰碰」的另一个隐藏能力逐渐被揭晓，彼此间的友谊也变得摇摇欲坠……那些深藏心底没说出口的话与渐行渐远的朋友，现在想起还会觉得遗憾吗？"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"心之觸碰","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"還無法完整表達自己想法的三位青梅竹馬的少年，遇到了具有神祕力量的生物，在人際關係複雜化的時代裡，找到「人與人的羈絆」，逐漸長大成人……"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"心之觸碰","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"秋、諒和優太是在同一座小島長大的兒時玩伴。​ 三人到了 20 歲的現在仍是摯友，一起在東京高田馬場生活。​ 他們還帶著一隻從島上帶出來的奇妙生物——「Fureru」。​ 透過類似心電感應的能力，「Fureru」讓嗜好、個性都不同的他們緊密聯繫。​ 只要觸碰身體，就能聽見對方的心聲——​ 這是隻有他們三人才知道的秘密。​ 然而，某起事件卻讓「Fureru」的另一個隱藏能力浮現，撼動了三人之間的友情。​"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"ฟูเรรุ ให้หัวใจจำ…ในวันที่เราเป็นเพื่อนกัน","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"กลุ่มเพื่อนในวัยเด็กได้พบกับสิ่งมีชีวิตลึกลับ ที่มีพลังพิเศษเชื่อมโยงจิตใจของพวกเขาไว้ด้วยกัน นำพาทั้งสามออกเดินทางเพื่อค้นหาความผูกพันที่ลึกซึ้ง... เกินกว่าคำว่า “มิตรภาพ”"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"Прикосновение","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"В бурном ритме токийской жизни трое студентов встречают загадочное существо с внешностью ежа и необычными сверхъестественными силами, которые меняют ход их судеб. Это помогает им раскрыть истинные узы дружбы и лучше понять самих себя."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Aki, Ryo và Yuta, những người bạn thời thơ ấu lớn lên trên cùng một hòn đảo, giờ đây đã 20 tuổi và bắt đầu sống cùng nhau tại Takadanobaba, Tokyo. Dù môi trường sống khác biệt: họ làm việc bán thời gian tại một quán bar, làm nhân viên bán hàng tại một công ty bất động sản, và là sinh viên tại một trường dạy nghề thiết kế thời trang, nhưng cả ba luôn có sự kết nối trong trái tim. Lý do là, những sinh vật bí ẩn được mang đến từ hòn đảo, Touch, sở hữu những năng lực bí ẩn tương tự như thần giao cách cảm, kết nối họ với những sở thích và tính cách khác nhau. Tình bạn giữa ba người lẽ ra phải tiếp tục, nhưng họ lại khám phá ra một sức mạnh tiềm ẩn khác của xúc giác…"},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"Fureru","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Gli amici d'infanzia incontrano una creatura dotata di poteri misteriosi che li spinge a scoprire i legami che uniscono i tre studenti."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Des amis d'enfance trouvent une créature dotée de pouvoirs mystérieux qui les pousse à découvrir les liens qui unissent les trois élèves."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Fureru","runtime":107,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://fureru-movie.com/","overview":"Durch das legendäre Wesen Fureru sind Aki, Ryou und Yuuta unzertrennlich. Doch es hat ein Geheimnis…"},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[{"id":1129610,"adult":false,"title":"BOCCHI THE ROCK! Recap Part 1","video":false,"overview":"Revisit events from Bocchi joining Kessoku Band to their first successful gig.","genre_ids":[16,35,10402],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.0946,"vote_count":27,"poster_path":"/gv5swmEUyrrTBuhNdb8rTCmsimm.jpg","release_date":"2024-06-07","vote_average":6.6,"backdrop_path":"/4px3C1MnKtshitubBXBJDS4Fo94.jpg","original_title":"劇場総集編ぼっち・ざ・ろっく！Re:","original_language":"ja"},{"id":128,"adult":false,"title":"Princess Mononoke","video":false,"overview":"Ashitaka, a prince of the disappearing Emishi people, is cursed by a demonized boar god and must journey to the west to find a cure. Along the way, he encounters San, a young human woman fighting to protect the forest, and Lady Eboshi, who is trying to destroy it. Ashitaka must find a way to bring balance to this conflict.","genre_ids":[12,14,16],"media_type":"movie","popularity":10.3567,"vote_count":8776,"poster_path":"/cMYCDADoLKLbB83g4WnJegaZimC.jpg","release_date":"1997-07-12","vote_average":8.323,"backdrop_path":"/gl0jzn4BupSbL2qMVeqrjKkF9Js.jpg","original_title":"もののけ姫","original_language":"ja"},{"id":105,"adult":false,"title":"Back to the Future","video":false,"overview":"Eighties teenager Marty McFly is accidentally sent back in time to 1955, inadvertently disrupting his parents' first meeting and attracting his mother's romantic interest. Marty must repair the damage to history by rekindling his parents' romance and - with the help of his eccentric inventor friend Doc Brown - return to 1985.","genre_ids":[12,35,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":17.301,"vote_count":21404,"poster_path":"/vN5B5WgYscRGcQpVhHl6p9DDTP0.jpg","release_date":"1985-07-03","vote_average":8.324,"backdrop_path":"/qskzmLTbarKnXDbo2HRj4NJ3vcW.jpg","original_title":"Back to the Future","original_language":"en"},{"id":597,"adult":false,"title":"Titanic","video":false,"overview":"101-year-old Rose DeWitt Bukater tells the story of her life aboard the Titanic, 84 years later. A young Rose boards the ship with her mother and fiancé. Meanwhile, Jack Dawson and Fabrizio De Rossi win third-class tickets aboard the ship. Rose tells the whole story from Titanic's departure through to its death—on its first and last voyage—on April 15, 1912.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":29.5562,"vote_count":26800,"poster_path":"/9xjZS2rlVxm8SFx8kPC3aIGCOYQ.jpg","release_date":"1997-12-18","vote_average":7.9,"backdrop_path":"/xnHVX37XZEp33hhCbYlQFq7ux1J.jpg","original_title":"Titanic","original_language":"en"},{"id":872585,"adult":false,"title":"Oppenheimer","video":false,"overview":"The story of J. Robert Oppenheimer's role in the development of the atomic bomb during World War II.","genre_ids":[18,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":21.4528,"vote_count":11366,"poster_path":"/8Gxv8gSFCU0XGDykEGv7zR1n2ua.jpg","release_date":"2023-07-19","vote_average":8.036,"backdrop_path":"/ycnO0cjsAROSGJKuMODgRtWsHQw.jpg","original_title":"Oppenheimer","original_language":"en"},{"id":475557,"adult":false,"title":"Joker","video":false,"overview":"During the 1980s, a failed stand-up comedian is driven insane and turns to a life of crime and chaos in Gotham City while becoming an infamous psychopathic crime figure.","genre_ids":[80,53,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":20.7457,"vote_count":27318,"poster_path":"/udDclJoHjfjb8Ekgsd4FDteOkCU.jpg","release_date":"2019-10-01","vote_average":8.128,"backdrop_path":"/hO7KbdvGOtDdeg0W4Y5nKEHeDDh.jpg","original_title":"Joker","original_language":"en"},{"id":466272,"adult":false,"title":"Once Upon a Time... in Hollywood","video":false,"overview":"Los Angeles, 1969. TV star Rick Dalton, a struggling actor specializing in westerns, and stuntman Cliff Booth, his best friend, try to survive in a constantly changing movie industry. Dalton is the neighbor of the young and promising actress and model Sharon Tate, who has just married the prestigious Polish director Roman Polanski…","genre_ids":[35,18,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":14.5698,"vote_count":14560,"poster_path":"/8j58iEBw9pOXFD2L0nt0ZXeHviB.jpg","release_date":"2019-07-24","vote_average":7.4,"backdrop_path":"/kKTPv9LKKs5L3oO1y5FNObxAPWI.jpg","original_title":"Once Upon a Time... in Hollywood","original_language":"en"},{"id":37165,"adult":false,"title":"The Truman Show","video":false,"overview":"An insurance salesman begins to suspect that his whole life is actually some sort of reality TV show.","genre_ids":[35,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":13.1631,"vote_count":19811,"poster_path":"/vuza0WqY239yBXOadKlGwJsZJFE.jpg","release_date":"1998-06-04","vote_average":8.151,"backdrop_path":"/aCHn2TXYJfzPXQKA6r9mKPbMlUB.jpg","original_title":"The Truman Show","original_language":"en"},{"id":272,"adult":false,"title":"Batman Begins","video":false,"overview":"Driven by tragedy, billionaire Bruce Wayne dedicates his life to uncovering and defeating the corruption that plagues his home, Gotham City.  Unable to work within the system, he instead creates a new identity, a symbol of fear for the criminal underworld - The Batman.","genre_ids":[18,80,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":16.9477,"vote_count":22268,"poster_path":"/sPX89Td70IDDjVr85jdSBb4rWGr.jpg","release_date":"2005-06-10","vote_average":7.721,"backdrop_path":"/9IIBboV7MCT0bTxzXHmWK1Hq558.jpg","original_title":"Batman Begins","original_language":"en"},{"id":278,"adult":false,"title":"The Shawshank Redemption","video":false,"overview":"Imprisoned in the 1940s for the double murder of his wife and her lover, upstanding banker Andy Dufresne begins a new life at the Shawshank prison, where he puts his accounting skills to work for an amoral warden. During his long stretch in prison, Dufresne comes to be admired by the other inmates -- including an older prisoner named Red -- for his integrity and unquenchable sense of hope.","genre_ids":[18,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":34.5879,"vote_count":29771,"poster_path":"/9cqNxx0GxF0bflZmeSMuL5tnGzr.jpg","release_date":"1994-09-23","vote_average":8.715,"backdrop_path":"/zfbjgQE1uSd9wiPTX4VzsLi0rGG.jpg","original_title":"The Shawshank Redemption","original_language":"en"},{"id":238,"adult":false,"title":"The Godfather","video":false,"overview":"Spanning the years 1945 to 1955, a chronicle of the fictional Italian-American Corleone crime family. When organized crime family patriarch, Vito Corleone barely survives an attempt on his life, his youngest son, Michael steps in to take care of the would-be killers, launching a campaign of bloody revenge.","genre_ids":[18,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":43.3138,"vote_count":22480,"poster_path":"/3bhkrj58Vtu7enYsRolD1fZdja1.jpg","release_date":"1972-03-14","vote_average":8.687,"backdrop_path":"/tSPT36ZKlP2WVHJLM4cQPLSzv3b.jpg","original_title":"The Godfather","original_language":"en"},{"id":11324,"adult":false,"title":"Shutter Island","video":false,"overview":"World War II soldier-turned-U.S. Marshal Teddy Daniels investigates the disappearance of a patient from a hospital for the criminally insane, but his efforts are compromised by troubling visions and a mysterious doctor.","genre_ids":[18,53,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":15.0553,"vote_count":25437,"poster_path":"/nrmXQ0zcZUL8jFLrakWc90IR8z9.jpg","release_date":"2010-02-14","vote_average":8.2,"backdrop_path":"/8xt8AMb1OKC63AdhNSaYBWxB4Iq.jpg","original_title":"Shutter Island","original_language":"en"},{"id":693134,"adult":false,"title":"Dune: Part Two","video":false,"overview":"Follow the mythic journey of Paul Atreides as he unites with Chani and the Fremen while on a path of revenge against the conspirators who destroyed his family. Facing a choice between the love of his life and the fate of the known universe, Paul endeavors to prevent a terrible future only he can foresee.","genre_ids":[878,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":23.1578,"vote_count":7534,"poster_path":"/1pdfLvkbY9ohJlCjQH2CZjjYVvJ.jpg","release_date":"2024-02-27","vote_average":8.131,"backdrop_path":"/ylkdrn23p3gQcHx7ukIfuy2CkTE.jpg","original_title":"Dune: Part Two","original_language":"en"},{"id":680,"adult":false,"title":"Pulp Fiction","video":false,"overview":"A burger-loving hit man, his philosophical partner, a drug-addled gangster's moll and a washed-up boxer converge in this sprawling, comedic crime caper. Their adventures unfurl in three stories that ingeniously trip back and forth in time.","genre_ids":[53,80,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":23.9216,"vote_count":29711,"poster_path":"/vQWk5YBFWF4bZaofAbv0tShwBvQ.jpg","release_date":"1994-09-10","vote_average":8.486,"backdrop_path":"/96hiUXEuYsu4tcnvlaY8tEMFM0m.jpg","original_title":"Pulp Fiction","original_language":"en"},{"id":10681,"adult":false,"title":"WALL·E","video":false,"overview":"After hundreds of years doing what he was built for, WALL•E— a robot designed to clean up the earth—discovers a new purpose in life when he meets a sleek search robot named EVE. EVE comes to realize that WALL•E has inadvertently stumbled upon the key to the planet's future, and races back to space to report to the humans. Meanwhile, WALL•E chases EVE across the galaxy and sets into motion one of the most imaginative adventures ever brought to the big screen.","genre_ids":[16,10751,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":12.9035,"vote_count":19935,"poster_path":"/hbhFnRzzg6ZDmm8YAmxBnQpQIPh.jpg","release_date":"2008-06-22","vote_average":8.108,"backdrop_path":"/fK5ssgvtI43z19FoWigdlqgpLRE.jpg","original_title":"WALL·E","original_language":"en"},{"id":65,"adult":false,"title":"8 Mile","video":false,"overview":"For Jimmy Smith, Jr., life is a daily fight just to keep hope alive. Feeding his dreams in Detroit's vibrant music scene, Jimmy wages an extraordinary personal struggle to find his own voice - and earn a place in a world where rhymes rule, legends are born and every moment… is another chance.","genre_ids":[18,10402],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.3758,"vote_count":7683,"poster_path":"/7BmQj8qE1FLuLTf7Xjf9sdIHzoa.jpg","release_date":"2002-11-08","vote_average":7.141,"backdrop_path":"/jNG7pl0DkN1nzxnbZj4MCGf2VEG.jpg","original_title":"8 Mile","original_language":"en"},{"id":2108,"adult":false,"title":"The Breakfast Club","video":false,"overview":"Five high school students from different walks of life endure a Saturday detention under a power-hungry principal. The di