mbark on their most dangerous mission yet: To track down a terrifying new weapon that threatens all of humanity before it falls into the wrong hands. With control of the future and the world's fate at stake and dark forces from Ethan's past closing in, a deadly race around the globe begins. Confronted by a mysterious, all-powerful enemy, Ethan must consider that nothing can matter more than his mission—not even the lives of those he cares about most.","genre_ids":[28,53,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":12.5395,"vote_count":4926,"poster_path":"/NNxYkU70HPurnNCSiCjYAmacwm.jpg","release_date":"2023-07-08","vote_average":7.507,"backdrop_path":"/628Dep6AxEtDxjZoGP78TsOxYbK.jpg","original_title":"Mission: Impossible - Dead Reckoning Part One","original_language":"en"}],"similar_content":[{"id":589972,"adult":false,"title":"Little Vampire","video":false,"overview":"Little Vampire lives in a haunted house with a merry group of monsters, but he is bored stiff! One night, he secretly sneaks out of the manor along with his trusted bulldog, Phantomato, on a quest to find some new friends.","genre_ids":[16,10751,14],"popularity":0.3631,"vote_count":43,"poster_path":"/mLd9FVJTwnPO3ERv82ea5IZo6Hl.jpg","release_date":"2020-10-21","vote_average":6.9,"backdrop_path":"/dAWrub4aTNMsh0pnYBiGPKZiREr.jpg","original_title":"Petit Vampire","original_language":"fr"},{"id":589973,"adult":false,"title":"SamSam","video":false,"overview":"SamSam, the smallest of the great heroes, has still not discovered his first superpower, while at home and at school, everyone has one! Faced with the worry of his parents and the mockery of his comrades, he goes in search of this hidden power. With the help of Mega, the new mysterious student of his school, Samsam embarks on this adventure full of cosmic monsters ...","genre_ids":[16,10751,878,12,35],"popularity":0.3545,"vote_count":14,"poster_path":"/nNMAglUfOuDuyAKYSmXzFkBeNha.jpg","release_date":"2020-02-05","vote_average":5.2,"backdrop_path":"/5T2kiBvi169qnCY8ul3btCRfJuf.jpg","original_title":"SamSam","original_language":"fr"},{"id":418956,"adult":false,"title":"The Ugly Duckling","video":false,"overview":"An outcast duckling's search for a family to accept him leads to constant rejection before learning his true identity as a swan.","genre_ids":[16,35],"popularity":0.9617,"vote_count":183,"poster_path":"/nCkMoq2penMxvdhQa0LGwK1G6fJ.jpg","release_date":"1939-04-07","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/woMB1t6cBbS9xPzZzsv8DI7IOxV.jpg","original_title":"The Ugly Duckling","original_language":"en"},{"id":647,"adult":false,"title":"Final Fantasy VII: Advent Children","video":false,"overview":"Two years have passed since the final battle with Sephiroth. Though Midgar, city of mako, city of prosperity, has been reduced to ruins, its people slowly but steadily walk the road to reconstruction. However, a mysterious illness called Geostigma torments them. With no cure in sight, it brings death to the afflicted, one after another, robbing the people of their fledgling hope.","genre_ids":[16,28,12,14,878],"popularity":2.093,"vote_count":1211,"poster_path":"/pTIXM2yu8McSlcQVs1VjVSNC45x.jpg","release_date":"2005-07-14","vote_average":7.161,"backdrop_path":"/8xhgpYyNSX5sJi0P35hwL73QYOV.jpg","original_title":"Final Fantasy VII: Advent Children","original_language":"ja"},{"id":421594,"adult":false,"title":"Nana and Kaoru","video":false,"overview":"Kaoru is a 17-year-old boy with an SM fetish, secretly dreaming of an SM relationship with his childhood friend Nana. One day Kaoru's mother asks Nana to hide all his SM toys so that he will study for a change. However, Nana finds the leather one-piece that Kaoru bought and tries it on, but she accidentally locks it and does not have the key! This is the beginning of a very strange relationship...","genre_ids":[16,35],"popularity":0.7443,"vote_count":20,"poster_path":"/qCWi9MHrRctaCR82Rw3SZH20P2i.jpg","release_date":"2011-03-29","vote_average":4.8,"backdrop_path":"/u7rRtrJqngEFmptLsXQayC2cP4r.jpg","original_title":"ナナとカオル","original_language":"ja"},{"id":766423,"adult":false,"title":"Puparia","video":false,"overview":"Something is about to change drastically, and the only thing to do is to witness it.","genre_ids":[16,18,14],"popularity":0.1282,"vote_count":59,"poster_path":"/3KRpbwNDrQ8cqKoVknoPqqtrpAO.jpg","release_date":"2021-09-23","vote_average":7.958,"backdrop_path":"/6HRvFDiP894qvRLMu0nM0WeNbiC.jpg","original_title":"Puparia","original_language":"ja"},{"id":949394,"adult":false,"title":"Ensemble Stars!! -Road to Show--","video":false,"overview":"Ensemble Square - a brand new building in the middle of the city where countless people come and go. It’s home to four offices belonging to idols who spend their days singing and dancing. Films starring the Ensemble Square idols have been nominated for the Idol Film Festival (IFF), an annual festival held in New York City, and representative idols are selected to attend. The boys jet off to NYC to attend the festival and reception party, and afterward, head out on the town to see the sights and sounds. But a suspicious shadow is creeping up on them…","genre_ids":[16],"popularity":0.7096,"vote_count":5,"poster_path":"/hW4Y4Fy8khf4D3tlvwV82txg1uy.jpg","release_date":"2022-03-04","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/eTfbiJANxSTnrISIL9JSGeI8uur.jpg","original_title":"あんさんぶるスターズ！！-Road to Show!!-","original_language":"ja"},{"id":919,"adult":false,"title":"Blood: The Last Vampire","video":false,"overview":"In Japan, the vampire-hunter Saya, who is a powerful original, is sent by her liaison with the government, David, posed as a teenage student to the Yokota High School on the eve of Halloween to hunt down vampires. Saya asks David to give a new katana to her. Soon she saves the school nurse Makiho Amano from two vampires disguised of classmates and Makiho witnesses her fight against the powerful demon.","genre_ids":[16,14,27],"popularity":1.1511,"vote_count":362,"poster_path":"/uRwR5lcl55n5JSaTiYPwp5KjP6A.jpg","release_date":"2000-11-18","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/17s9ojb8j8QnBGCfqDUJraXLlFi.jpg","original_title":"BLOOD THE LAST VAMPIRE","original_language":"ja"},{"id":1293708,"adult":false,"title":"AIKa: Special Trial","video":false,"overview":"An OVA released between episodes 5 and 6 of AIKa, that takes place between episodes 4 and 5.","genre_ids":[16,878,35],"popularity":0.2816,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/vLGtkrfmRqFh536eGmPpOUaLJiJ.jpg","release_date":"1998-05-25","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"AIKa Special TRIAL","original_language":"ja"},{"id":249287,"adult":false,"title":"Zillion: Burning Night","video":false,"overview":"In the 24th century, on the war-torn planet Maris the conniving Queen Adama abducts Apple, a member of an heroic trio known as the White Knights, and imprisons her in the infamous Zone. Even though no one has ever returned alive from the Zone — and despite the low ammo at their disposal — the other knights follow their companion. What they find there, however, is an enigmatic figure with a mind-bending revelation...","genre_ids":[16,12,878],"popularity":0.4353,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":"/bV4l7hbYU6kwreyLQaIvmbzeh6C.jpg","release_date":"1988-06-21","vote_average":7.8,"backdrop_path":"/Ar0z41ErRQF9JqBG2LYyj8zXujX.jpg","original_title":"赤い光弾ジリオン 歌姫夜曲","original_language":"ja"},{"id":823,"adult":false,"title":"Jin-Roh: The Wolf Brigade","video":false,"overview":"A member of an elite paramilitary counter-terrorism unit becomes traumatized after witnessing the suicide bombing of a young girl and is forced to undergo retraining. However, unbeknownst to him, he becomes a key player in a dispute between rival police divisions, as he finds himself increasingly involved with the sister of the girl he saw die.","genre_ids":[16,18,10749,53,878],"popularity":2.1022,"vote_count":540,"poster_path":"/63EMBxmcafkc4cWuUWQh2Ttd2jh.jpg","release_date":"1999-11-17","vote_average":7.408,"backdrop_path":"/2WuR3EaBj8X2WR4fvqa449tnNLn.jpg","original_title":"人狼 JIN-ROH","original_language":"ja"},{"id":1309514,"adult":false,"title":"Let's Go! Anpanman: Baikinman and Lulun","video":false,"overview":"One day, Baikinman finds a picture book, hears a voice calling for help from inside the book, and is sucked into the book, where he meets the forest fairy Lulun. Lulun, who is too scared to muster up the courage, asks her to defeat the \"Sucking Elephant\" that is rampaging in the forest. Although Lulun is reluctant at first, she gains courage when she sees Baikinman standing up to Suitoruzo, but she is forced to struggle against Suitoruzo's strength. In a desperate situation, Baikinman tells Lulun to call Anpanman, but...","genre_ids":[16,14,10751],"popularity":0.5219,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/3ItSSPlWjPhwru07yJR2VclJW5P.jpg","release_date":"2024-06-28","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":"/iUpxdFsfF5NBm2lAbTkoBYPqh9D.jpg","original_title":"それいけ！アンパンマン ばいきんまんとえほんのルルン","original_language":"ja"},{"id":16767,"adult":false,"title":"Spriggan","video":false,"overview":"An elite superhuman agent must stop a foreign military unit from seizing control of an ancient artifact that holds the key to ultimate power.","genre_ids":[28,16,878],"popularity":1.2157,"vote_count":104,"poster_path":"/nX2sgumjpBkEMzGFSMdBZMCiVgX.jpg","release_date":"1998-09-05","vote_average":6.1,"backdrop_path":"/bDp6VdcKC6JuSqaM86GSD3KPGa3.jpg","original_title":"スプリガン","original_language":"ja"},{"id":16859,"adult":false,"title":"Kiki's Delivery Service","video":false,"overview":"A young witch, on her mandatory year of independent life, finds fitting into a new community difficult while she supports herself by running an air courier service.","genre_ids":[16,10751,14,18],"popularity":5.6261,"vote_count":4459,"poster_path":"/Aufa4YdZIv4AXpR9rznwVA5SEfd.jpg","release_date":"1989-07-29","vote_average":7.83,"backdrop_path":"/h5pAEVma835u8xoE60kmLVopLct.jpg","original_title":"魔女の宅急便","original_language":"ja"},{"id":16860,"adult":false,"title":"RahXephon: Pluralitas Concentio","video":false,"overview":"Ayato and Haruka are middle-school sweethearts whose lives take a dire turn when the mysterious Mu invade Tokyo in the year 2012. Protecting humanity from the Mu may be Ayato's destiny, but what he really wants is to regain the relationship he once had with Haruka... a love that will have to transcend space, time, and reality itself.","genre_ids":[16,878],"popularity":0.9444,"vote_count":13,"poster_path":"/wK8yAt16bfQBaKBatAJxYRdpu9Y.jpg","release_date":"2003-04-19","vote_average":5.8,"backdrop_path":"/nlvmh1r91egemTd1QksOyptHcO7.jpg","original_title":"ラーゼフォン 多元変奏曲","original_language":"ja"},{"id":16907,"adult":false,"title":"Naruto the Movie: Ninja Clash in the Land of Snow","video":false,"overview":"Naruto is thrilled when he is sent on a mission to protect his favorite actress, Yukie Fujikaze, on the set of her new movie, The Adventures of Princess Gale. But when the crew ventures out to film in the icy, foreboding Land of Snow, Yukie mysteriously flees! Naruto and his squad set off to find her... unaware that three Snow Ninja lie in wait, with a sinister purpose that will force Yukie to face her hidden past!","genre_ids":[35,28,16,12],"popularity":5.4319,"vote_count":603,"poster_path":"/eUNRUeSNzm8LktH4HRaYiAReB6R.jpg","release_date":"2004-08-21","vote_average":7.299,"backdrop_path":"/bW0Hr19Xo7LDnMmywXuH5YoTMY5.jpg","original_title":"劇場版 NARUTO 大活劇! 雪姫忍法帖だってばよ!!","original_language":"ja"},{"id":16910,"adult":false,"title":"Naruto the Movie: Legend of the Stone of Gelel","video":false,"overview":"Naruto, Shikamaru, and Sakura are executing their mission of delivering a lost pet to a certain village. However, right in the midst of things, troops led by the mysterious knight, Temujin, attack them. In the violent battle, the three become separated. Temujin challenges Naruto to a fight and at the end of the fierce battle, both fall together from a high cliff...","genre_ids":[16,12,14],"popularity":4.9032,"vote_count":430,"poster_path":"/itKMldwL6uhUZYO3X78NOFU4zzO.jpg","release_date":"2005-08-06","vote_average":6.795,"backdrop_path":"/ldwWnaWoW8ziEFflimoraZouyvB.jpg","original_title":"劇場版 NARUTO -ナルト- 大激突!幻の地底遺跡だってばよ","original_language":"ja"},{"id":16224,"adult":false,"title":"Plastic Little: The Adventures of Captain Tita","video":false,"overview":"Tita, captain of a pet-hunting ship for the galaxy’s upper class, finds herself babysitting Elysse, a scientist’s daughter being pursued by the military commander Lord Guizel, who’ll stop at nothing to retrieve the key to the high-powered weapon her father created. Dodging the lord’s clutches is a planet-wide game of cat and mouse for Tita and her crew, with one crucial difference: Mice don’t shoot back!","genre_ids":[16,878,12,35],"popularity":1.3143,"vote_count":27,"poster_path":"/de1dPo7MUK1NvBntnshzzVmi84e.jpg","release_date":"1994-03-21","vote_average":5.6,"backdrop_path":"/9iJdPijw8bc8VpPp00u2OMnA8oe.jpg","original_title":"プラスチックリトル","original_language":"ja"},{"id":16228,"adult":false,"title":"Street Fighter Alpha: Generations","video":false,"overview":"When Ryu returns to pay homage to his deceased mentor, Gouken, he is tormented by disturbing memories of his master's killer (Gouki). In a quest to become a true martial arts master, he sets out to hone his street fighting skills and deliver himself from the haunting legacy of the dark hadou.","genre_ids":[28,16],"popularity":0.5441,"vote_count":80,"poster_path":"/z6amRu0MxrBz1I3oLJz6pkSveG9.jpg","release_date":"2005-10-25","vote_average":6.9,"backdrop_path":"/rAAHFRkY4EVlj7pE5aLY44zHY03.jpg","original_title":"Street Fighter Alpha: Generations","original_language":"en"},{"id":16308,"adult":false,"title":"Mobile Suit Gundam F91","video":false,"overview":"U.C. 0123. After a generation of peace, the Earth Federation has begun to build new space colonies to house humanity's growing population. But a new force, the aristocratic Crossbone Vanguard, plans to seize the colonies of the newly constructed Frontier Side for itself. As their home becomes a battlefield, a handful of young civilians struggle to escape the conflict. To save his friends and family, the reluctant warrior Seabook Arno becomes the pilot of a new Gundam which bears the code name F91.","genre_ids":[16,878],"popularity":4.5973,"vote_count":48,"poster_path":"/eGwwFG9mMEXDEQ70bSSqAzCY3Dc.jpg","release_date":"1991-03-16","vote_average":6.51,"backdrop_path":"/3m6rRRxJl7nzcLiNbA3TfQE7UZX.jpg","original_title":"機動戦士ガンダムF91","original_language":"ja"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt30317151","twitter_id":"fureru_movie","facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":"Q123857583","instagram_id":null},"social_ids":{"twitter":"fureru_movie","facebook":null,"instagram":null},"gdvg_id":110693,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_episode_guide":null,"wiki_production":null,"wiki_cast_notes":null,"wiki_reception":null,"wiki_soundtrack":null,"wiki_release":null,"wiki_accolades":null,"release_dates":[{"iso_3166_1":"BR","release_dates":[{"note":"Crunchyroll","type":4,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2026-01-15T00:00:00.000Z","certification":"14"}]},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","release_dates":[{"note":"10 cities release","type":2,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2025-04-18T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""},{"note":"","type":3,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2025-04-19T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""}]},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":3,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2025-05-22T00:00:00.000Z","certification":"I"}]},{"iso_3166_1":"IT","release_dates":[{"note":"24FRAME Future Film Fest","type":1,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2025-04-12T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""}]},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","release_dates":[{"note":"Tokyo","type":1,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2024-09-16T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""},{"note":"","type":3,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2024